    <item>
      <title>随着不确定性的消退，巴西央行将保持降息步伐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/brazil-to-cut-interest-rate-by-half-point</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着全球前景的不确定性消退和当地通胀进一步放缓，巴西央行将连续第四次降息 50 个基点，并逐步推进货币宽松政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/brazil-to-cut-interest-rate-by-half-point</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
